  "title": "Events & Marketing Representative",
  "description": "<p>INNOVATION MARKETING ORGANISATION</p><p>Looking out for Events & Marketing representative! (Only Singaporeans)</p><p>We are part of a regional outsource events & marketing company, currently located in Singapore, Malaysia, Taiwan and hongkong. Where we work closely with clients to provide marketing solutions, increases market shares and creating brand awareness.</p><p>We are looking out for potential candidate to join us in our expansion plans:</p><p>As long as you are:</p><p>- FUN</p><p>- Willing to Learn</p><p>- A Team Player</p><p>- Competitive</p><p>Benefits:</p><p>- No experience needed</p><p>- Leadership and guidance</p><p>- Traveling Opportunities </p><p>- Self development</p><p>- Advancement</p><p>- WORKING WITH FUN PEOPLE!</p>",
